gutls/UcR5rLX3EdI/AAAAAAAAj-I/9zq-Kb1P2Yc/s320/P1020421.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-44LpaYc500U/UcR5xSTH0hI/AAAAAAAAj-Y/EKOq9I_8oMU/s1600/P1020423.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-44LpaYc500U/UcR5xSTH0hI/AAAAAAAAj-Y/EKOq9I_8oMU/s1600/P1020423.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-dnfT9lWgpC0/UcR54-OfVbI/AAAAAAAAj-g/B6jiCuZt1d4/s1600/%E6%9D%8E%E6%B0%91%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%B6.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-dnfT9lWgpC0/UcR54-OfVbI/AAAAAAAAj-g/B6jiCuZt1d4/s320/%E6%9D%8E%E6%B0%91%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%B6.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>李民的家</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-el966rhZrCo/UcR5-ke6xEI/AAAAAAAAj-4/esOjUCC3x5E/s1600/%E9%99%86%E9%9B%85%E7%BE%8E%E5%AE%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E9%80%BC%E8%BF%AB%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E8%87%B3%E4%BB%8A%E5%B7%B218%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%88.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-el966rhZrCo/UcR5-ke6xEI/AAAAAAAAj-4/esOjUCC3x5E/s320/%E9%99%86%E9%9B%85%E7%BE%8E%E5%AE%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E9%80%BC%E8%BF%AB%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E8%87%B3%E4%BB%8A%E5%B7%B218%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%88.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>陆雅美家的房屋逼迫停止施工至今已18个月</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-0nljRDwAJMM/UcR57A7-wQI/AAAAAAAAj-o/m_vAs9Cx64M/s1600/%E9%99%86%E9%9B%85%E7%BE%8E%E5%AE%B6%E6%AD%A3%E5%9C%A8%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E8%A2%AB%E6%AF%81%E5%9D%8FP1020400.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-0nljRDwAJMM/UcR57A7-wQI/AAAAAAAAj-o/m_vAs9Cx64M/s320/%E9%99%86%E9%9B%85%E7%BE%8E%E5%AE%B6%E6%AD%A3%E5%9C%A8%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E8%A2%AB%E6%AF%81%E5%9D%8FP1020400.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-TlOjx-EkUUQ/UcR5-LuH8xI/AAAAAAAAj-w/Rx2LjTIe3UI/s1600/%E7%9E%A7%EF%BC%9A%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E8%BF%99%E4%BD%8D%E7%A9%BF%E7%99%BD%E8%A1%A3%E6%9C%8D%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%B8%82%E5%AE%9D%E5%B1%B1%E5%8C%BA%E7%BD%97%E5%BA%97%E9%95%87%E5%BC%A0%E5%A3%AB%E6%9D%91%E6%9D%91%E5%B9%B2%E9%83%A8%E8%AF%B4%E2%80%9C%E6%98%AF%E6%8B%86%E6%88%BF%E9%98%9F%E8%AE%A9%E6%88%91%E7%AD%BE%E5%AD%97%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9D.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-TlOjx-EkUUQ/UcR5-LuH8xI/AAAAAAAAj-w/Rx2LjTIe3UI/s320/%E7%9E%A7%EF%BC%9A%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E8%BF%99%E4%BD%8D%E7%A9%BF%E7%99%BD%E8%A1%A3%E6%9C%8D%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%B8%82%E5%AE%9D%E5%B1%B1%E5%8C%BA%E7%BD%97%E5%BA%97%E9%95%87%E5%BC%A0%E5%A3%AB%E6%9D%91%E6%9D%91%E5%B9%B2%E9%83%A8%E8%AF%B4%E2%80%9C%E6%98%AF%E6%8B%86%E6%88%BF%E9%98%9F%E8%AE%A9%E6%88%91%E7%AD%BE%E5%AD%97%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9D.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>穿白衣的罗店镇张士村村干部说：是拆房队让我签字的</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-QZuImxRp-P0/UcR6G2AXinI/AAAAAAAAj_A/6mYAyZ78tXw/s1600/%E5%A3%B0%E6%8F%B4%E5%90%8D%E5%8D%95%E3%80%80.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-QZuImxRp-P0/UcR6G2AXinI/AAAAAAAAj_A/6mYAyZ78tXw/s320/%E5%A3%B0%E6%8F%B4%E5%90%8D%E5%8D%95%E3%80%80.jpg\" width=\"232\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/p